            }


## Add Shoppinglists [/shoppinglists/]            

### Add a shoppinglist [POST]

You add a shoppinglist using this action. It takes a JSON
object containing the name of the shoppinglist and description and
Authenication token in header

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            x-access-token: Token
    + Body

            {
                "newlist": "Shoes"
                
            }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /shoppinglists/

    + Body

            {
                'Shoes': 'created'
            
            }


### Retrieve shoppinglists [GET/shoppinglists/]

You can retrieve shoppinglists using this action. 
Request contains Authenication token in header

    + Headers

            x-access-token: Token

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /shoppinglists/?each_page=1&page_number=1

    + Body

            {
                "lists":[
                            "Shoes"
                        ]
            }



### Retrieve a single shoppinglists [GET/shoppinglist/]

You retrieve a single shoppinglist using this action. 
Request contains Authenication token in header

    + Headers

            x-access-token: Token

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /shoppinglist/trousers?each_page=1&page_number=1

    + Body

            {
                "Products": [
                             {
                                "Amountspent": 400,
                                "Product": "nike",
                                "Quantity": 5
                                }
                            ]
            }

### Update a shoppinglist [PUT]

You update a shoppinglist using this action. 
Request contains Authenication token in header

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            x-access-token: Token
        
    + Body

            {
                "newName": "Trousers",
               
            }


+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /shoppinglists/id

    + Body

            {
                'message':'The product has been updated'
            }

### Delete a shoppinglist [DELETE]

You delete a shoppinglist using this action. 
Request contains Authenication token in header


    + Headers

            x-access-token: Token
        

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /shoppinglists/id

    + Body

            {
                "Message":"The list name has been deleted"
            }

## Add Items [/shoppinglists/id/items]            

### Add an item [POST]

You add an item using this action. It takes a JSON
object containing an item name

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            x-access-token: Token
    + Body

            {   "product":"nike",
                "Quantity":5,
                "Amountspent":400
            }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /shoppinglists/id/items

    + Body

            {
                'Message': 'The product has been added',
                
            }

## Items [/shoppinglists/id/items/item_id]            

